description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Scheme Access Team is pleased to be able to offer two exciting opportunities for self-motivated, accurate and enthusiastic individuals as Scheme Access Administrators.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The posts are permanent.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;You will work alongside established and experienced Scheme Access colleagues. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;The team is responsible for ensuring that correct access into the NHS Pension Scheme is granted for NHS employers. The post holders will process NHS Pensions Scheme Access applications, associated casework and related correspondence. This will involve dealing with current and retrospective enquiries from both internal and external customers and will require routine&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;analysis, investigation and reconciliation of information. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Further comprehensive information regarding the role and the expectations required are held within the content of the accompanying Scheme Access Team Administrator Job Description and Person Specification.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameElizabeth ChapmanJob titleOperations ManagerEmail addressElizabeth.chapman3@nhs.netAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
